item.title: 25 Before 25: Update #2
item.description: When I turned 22 I made a bucket list of things to accomplish by the time I’m 25. Right now I’m 23 years old. There is a year and a half until I am 25. Let’s see how I’m progressing with my bucket list! 1.Graduate from university: Done! 2. Move out: Still working on it! I need a full-time job first before that happens. 3. Max out my TFSA: Slowly but surely.
